        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(gateway): honor configured remote probe budgets",
        "body": "## Summary\n- honor the caller timeout budget for configured remote and explicit remote gateway probes\n- keep the shorter ssh tunnel cap unchanged\n- cover both the helper budget split and the `gateway probe` command path with regression tests\n\nFixes #65355.\n\n## Proof\n\n### Behavior addressed\n`openclaw gateway probe --timeout <n>` still capped `configRemote` probes at `1500ms`, so a healthy remote gateway could false-negative even when the caller supplied a larger budget.\n\n### Real environment tested\n- Targeted Vitest coverage for the command path that wires `gateway probe --timeout` into `probeGateway()`\n- Source-level regression coverage for the exact `configRemote` and `explicit` budget calculation\n\n### Exact steps or command run after this patch\nCurrent HEAD: `6f4d61da72ccdac1e6ad1fa4e5fa9f691780127e`\n\n```bash\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs   src/commands/gateway-status/helpers.test.ts   src/commands/gateway-status.test.ts\n```\n\n### Evidence after fix\n- `resolveProbeBudgetMs(15000, { kind: \"configRemote\", ... })` now returns `15000`\n- `resolveProbeBudgetMs(15000, { kind: \"explicit\", ... })` now returns `15000`\n- ssh tunnel probes still cap at `2000`\n- `runGatewayStatus(..., { timeout: \"15000\" })` now passes `timeoutMs=15000` to a configured remote target\n\n### Observed result after fix\n\nRe-run on rebased HEAD `6f4d61da72ccdac1e6ad1fa4e5fa9f691780127e` (based on `origin/main` `462e315953`):\n\n```text\n$ OPENCLAW_VITEST_MAX_WORKERS=1 node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run \\\n    --config test/vitest/vitest.commands.config.ts \\\n    src/commands/gateway-status.test.ts --reporter=dot\n Test Files  1 passed (1)\n      Tests  25 passed (25)\n\n$ OPENCLAW_VITEST_MAX_WORKERS=1 node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run \\\n    --config test/vitest/vitest.unit-fast.config.ts \\\n    src/commands/gateway-status/helpers.test.ts --reporter=dot\n Test Files  1 passed (1)\n      Tests  17 passed (17)\n\nTotal: 2 test files, 42 tests passed\n```\n\n### What was not tested\n- I did not rerun the reporter's live macOS-to-remote WSS environment end to end in this workspace.\n",
